1
00:00:15,123 --> 00:00:16,840
Mr. Perm loves you so much.

2
00:00:17,050 --> 00:00:19,510
He can do everything in his power to make you happy.

3
00:00:19,843 --> 00:00:21,480
He can't do everything.

4
00:00:21,863 --> 00:00:24,240
If that so, is there anything I can do on his behalf?

5
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:26,200
You can let me know.

6
00:00:26,377 --> 00:00:27,400
I will do it for you.

7
00:00:27,757 --> 00:00:29,120
You can't do this for him.

8
00:00:30,920 --> 00:00:34,240
Can you dance with my daughter?

9
00:00:34,450 --> 00:00:35,720
With my pleasure, Your Highness.

10
00:00:35,883 --> 00:00:37,000
I feel bad for her.

11
00:00:37,177 --> 00:00:39,490
Her husband didn't even want to dance with her.

12
00:00:40,290 --> 00:00:42,080
M.R. Anongnuch.

13
00:00:42,480 --> 00:00:43,800
Can I have my husband back?

14
00:00:44,443 --> 00:00:46,120
Where are your manners?

15
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:47,401
You should wait for me outside.

16
00:00:47,817 --> 00:00:49,920
Ms. Shen, what happened? Where is Mr. Perm?

17
00:00:50,110 --> 00:00:52,200
I think you should take me home.

18
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:55,521
This is your favorite dance. It's waltz.

19
00:00:55,650 --> 00:00:57,520
Why don't you get back inside and dance for a song?

20
00:00:57,817 --> 00:00:58,818
We can just dance here.

21
00:01:26,337 --> 00:01:27,338
Shen?

22
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,560
Shen? Where are you?

23
00:01:34,483 --> 00:01:35,640
I'm taking you to dance.

24
00:01:36,183 --> 00:01:37,600
- Shen!
- Mr. Perm.

25
00:01:38,650 --> 00:01:39,720
Are you looking for Ms. Shen?

26
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:41,081
Did you see her?

27
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:43,000
I saw her walking over there.

28
00:01:43,503 --> 00:01:44,520
I can take you.

29
00:01:47,130 --> 00:01:48,131
Wait.

30
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,720
What did you do?

31
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:04,321
Earlier…

32
00:02:04,563 --> 00:02:06,880
I leaned against a tree to rest, sir.

33
00:02:09,040 --> 00:02:10,200
I can take you to see her.

34
00:03:00,690 --> 00:03:02,680
Maybe she went back to the party inside.

35
00:03:04,690 --> 00:03:05,760
Where is she?

36
00:03:07,357 --> 00:03:08,358
I'm right here.

37
00:03:13,648 --> 00:03:14,680
What are you doing in the car like that?

38
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:21,530
Come on, let's go back to the party.

39
00:03:22,690 --> 00:03:23,691
I don't think so.

40
00:03:24,423 --> 00:03:27,240
I'm not in the moed to dance, I'd rather go home.

41
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,920
I introduced you in a big party

42
00:03:30,263 --> 00:03:31,480
because I wanted you to start socializing.

43
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:32,841
Instead, you wanted to go home?

44
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,600
Let's get back inside with me.

45
00:03:37,343 --> 00:03:39,960
I'm tired, I want to go home.

46
00:03:51,017 --> 00:03:53,400
Suit yourself. Let's go.

47
00:03:55,343 --> 00:03:57,270
Tone, let's go home.

48
00:03:57,790 --> 00:03:58,791
Yes, sir.

49
00:04:51,563 --> 00:04:53,710
How were the ladies that I introduced you to earlier?

50
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:55,040
Was it fun chatting with them?

51
00:04:57,201 --> 00:04:58,202
Fine, I guess.

52
00:05:00,997 --> 00:05:04,720
You need to socialize with others in the next event.

53
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:08,360
I saw you sitting by yourself, not talking to anyone.

54
00:05:10,523 --> 00:05:11,524
Sure.

55
00:05:13,937 --> 00:05:16,000
You haven't talked much to you, are you still mad at me?

56
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:21,441
Nope, just really tired.

57
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,640
Are you jealous of me and Nuch?

58
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,840
Whatever you say.

59
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,760
Nope, we can't do this.

60
00:07:33,343 --> 00:07:35,080
No matter how mean my husband is to me,

61
00:07:36,190 --> 00:07:37,560
I can't do this to him.

62
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,601
Shen?

63
00:07:43,437 --> 00:07:45,200
- Shen? Where are you?
- Ms. Shen.

64
00:07:46,817 --> 00:07:47,840
I'm taking you to dance.

65
00:07:48,210 --> 00:07:49,360
- Shen!
- Shh!

66
00:07:52,217 --> 00:07:55,040
Mr. Perm, are you looking for Ms. Shen?

67
00:07:55,483 --> 00:07:56,484
Did you see her?

68
00:07:56,877 --> 00:07:58,878
I saw her walking over there a few minutes ago.

69
00:09:43,057 --> 00:09:45,760
You both disobeyed my orders last night.

70
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,520
You disrespected me

71
00:09:49,003 --> 00:09:51,042
still you've got a nerve to sit with me for breakfast.

72
00:09:53,037 --> 00:09:54,038
Mom,

73
00:09:54,843 --> 00:09:57,560
nobody said bad thing about Shen's dress last night.

74
00:09:58,443 --> 00:10:00,400
Prince Pin said that her dress was beautiful.

75
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:02,100
What more do you want from us?

76
00:10:03,650 --> 00:10:06,000
How did you know that nobody say bad things about her dress?

77
00:10:07,390 --> 00:10:09,360
A noble person won't say bad things about you right in front of you.

78
00:10:12,057 --> 00:10:14,440
I guess we have become a talk of the town already,

79
00:10:14,683 --> 00:10:17,320
they'd say that I didn't teach my daughter-in-law

80
00:10:17,497 --> 00:10:19,321
how to dress appropriately.

81
00:10:20,417 --> 00:10:21,920
I'm done eating. I need to get to work.

82
00:10:23,837 --> 00:10:25,080
You should go out today,

83
00:10:25,337 --> 00:10:27,600
don't get in her way or you two will fight again.

84
00:10:29,338 --> 00:10:31,960
I'm so tired to intervene when the in-laws are fighting.

85
00:10:33,237 --> 00:10:34,920
Perm! Perm!

86
00:10:35,357 --> 00:10:36,960
What do you mean by that?

87
00:10:37,257 --> 00:10:39,040
Are you berating me?

88
00:10:42,103 --> 00:10:43,204
Are you happy now?

89
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:45,400
For causing an argument among a mother and her son.

90
00:10:50,050 --> 00:10:52,750
I'm done eating too. Excuse me.

91
00:10:58,103 --> 00:11:00,200
You can try avoiding me, Shen.

92
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:58,040
Are you looking for something, Ms. Shen?

93
00:12:04,737 --> 00:12:07,680
I was just getting some fresh air.

94
00:12:09,137 --> 00:12:11,520
Should we harvest flowers in the garden?

95
00:12:11,570 --> 00:12:13,100
We can put them in a vase to brighten up the room.

96
00:12:31,090 --> 00:12:32,091
Ms. Shen.

97
00:12:32,637 --> 00:12:34,900
Why this pomegranate tree from your house

98
00:12:34,938 --> 00:12:36,600
doesn't produce any fruits or flowers?

99
00:12:39,617 --> 00:12:41,360
It can feel the different soil and air, I guess.

100
00:12:42,363 --> 00:12:43,840
Let it adjust a little.

101
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,960
Fruits and flowers will flourish after.

102
00:12:50,103 --> 00:12:51,104
Chan,

103
00:12:51,923 --> 00:12:54,360
we need your help in the kitchen. Khunying keeps on complaining.

104
00:12:54,737 --> 00:12:55,738
She is?

105
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:57,520
I'm sorry, Ms. Shen.

106
00:12:57,957 --> 00:12:59,840
- It's okay.
- I'm going!

107
00:13:01,383 --> 00:13:03,040
I really need to go.

108
00:13:03,203 --> 00:13:04,204
I understand.

109
00:13:25,523 --> 00:13:26,682
What are you trying to do?

110
00:13:30,523 --> 00:13:32,880
- What is wrong with you?
- You're avoiding me.

111
00:13:34,023 --> 00:13:35,024
I am not.

112
00:13:35,543 --> 00:13:37,700
Why did you act like you didn't want to see me?

113
00:13:39,743 --> 00:13:41,300
I have nothing to talk to you.

114
00:13:42,283 --> 00:13:43,284
Ms. Shen,

115
00:13:44,650 --> 00:13:46,151
are you mad at me about last night?

116
00:13:46,210 --> 00:13:47,211
Stop saying that.

117
00:13:48,863 --> 00:13:50,720
You need to forget about last night,

118
00:13:51,503 --> 00:13:52,640
and don't talk about it anymore.

119
00:13:54,603 --> 00:13:55,800
It never happened.

120
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:07,480
I'm sorry.

121
00:14:10,160 --> 00:14:12,320
I didn't expect that you would be so upset about it.

122
00:14:16,170 --> 00:14:17,960
I just feel bad for my husband.

123
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:27,360
What do you feel about me?

124
00:14:46,370 --> 00:14:47,371
Come in.

125
00:14:53,417 --> 00:14:55,280
Khunying asked to see you at the hall, ma'am.

126
00:14:56,963 --> 00:14:58,083
I will be right there.

127
00:15:22,797 --> 00:15:23,798
Rayrai!

128
00:15:27,570 --> 00:15:29,623
Ms. Rayrai! Ms. Rayrai!

129
00:15:31,160 --> 00:15:32,161
Call the doctor.

130
00:15:32,703 --> 00:15:34,280
- Go!
- Yes, sir.

131
00:15:34,917 --> 00:15:35,918
Ms. Rayrai!

132
00:15:48,720 --> 00:15:50,480
How's my wife, Doc?

133
00:15:51,350 --> 00:15:53,600
She is doing fine, just some bruises on her.

134
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:55,440
But her baby…

135
00:15:58,120 --> 00:16:01,240
Rayrai! You should have been more careful.

136
00:16:01,637 --> 00:16:03,040
What were you thinking, felling down the stairs like that.

137
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:06,400
Don't blame her. It's an accident.

138
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:09,281
Rayrai said that she slipped and fell.

139
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,840
Nobody never slipped on the stairs before.

140
00:16:12,291 --> 00:16:13,840
Why did she slip all of a sudden?

141
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:16,240
Well, I…

142
00:16:17,537 --> 00:16:19,560
I cleaned the stairs earlier

143
00:16:20,190 --> 00:16:23,080
and I saw mashed pumpkin on the floor.

144
00:16:28,197 --> 00:16:30,400
Why did the mashed pumpkin end up on the floor?

145
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:44,320
I didn't do it, honestly.

146
00:16:44,763 --> 00:16:47,200
I went to feed Khunphra this morning.

147
00:16:47,410 --> 00:16:48,760
If I really dropped the pumpkin,

148
00:16:48,850 --> 00:16:50,251
I would clean it up immediately.

149
00:16:50,423 --> 00:16:51,520
I wouldn't let the mess on the floor for so long.

150
00:16:52,323 --> 00:16:54,800
That's right. That is how normal people would do.

151
00:16:54,863 --> 00:16:56,720
When they make a mess, they need to clean it up.

152
00:16:57,550 --> 00:16:59,960
Unless you have bad intentions, so you leave the mess like that.

153
00:17:00,923 --> 00:17:02,960
There is no reason for me to do so.

154
00:17:03,800 --> 00:17:04,920
Who would know?

155
00:17:05,477 --> 00:17:07,440
You could have a fight with Rayrai earlier.

156
00:17:07,657 --> 00:17:09,960
Mom, don't accuse her like that.

157
00:17:10,550 --> 00:17:12,960
Shen wouldn't know when Rayrai would walk pass the area.

158
00:17:13,937 --> 00:17:15,640
Even if she really dropped the pumpkin,

159
00:17:15,700 --> 00:17:16,801
she did it intentionally

160
00:17:16,824 --> 00:17:18,320
and Rayrai just happened to be there.

161
00:17:18,437 --> 00:17:19,438
That's it.

162
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:22,440
Intentionally or not,

163
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:25,241
Shen is the one who caused Rayrai to fall down the stairs.

164
00:17:25,560 --> 00:17:26,561
Will you admit it?

165
00:17:26,717 --> 00:17:28,680
Why did you keep pushing it?

166
00:17:28,843 --> 00:17:30,177
It is an accident.

167
00:17:30,190 --> 00:17:31,640
It was my first baby.

168
00:17:31,783 --> 00:17:33,040
If it was your own baby, would you be mad?

169
00:17:33,163 --> 00:17:34,360
Come on, stop it!

170
00:17:35,237 --> 00:17:36,238
Did you see that?

171
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:38,880
You caused the whole house to be mad at each other.

172
00:17:43,270 --> 00:17:45,560
Fine. I am the one who dropped the pumpkin.

173
00:17:46,370 --> 00:17:48,240
If it will make you all to be happier,

174
00:17:48,560 --> 00:17:49,800
then I admit that I did it.

175
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:52,120
Are you all happier now?

176
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:59,360
Look! Look at what she just did.

177
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:03,040
I shouldn't have let that unlucky girl to live in the house.

178
00:18:03,790 --> 00:18:04,791
She has caused all the problems.

179
00:18:30,120 --> 00:18:31,121
You should rest.

180
00:18:32,077 --> 00:18:35,000
The doctor said you need to rest more so your body could recover.

181
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:37,560
I couldn't sleep.

182
00:18:38,650 --> 00:18:41,120
When I close my eyes, all I think about is the baby

183
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:43,840
Can you stay with me a little longer?

184
00:18:47,097 --> 00:18:48,280
I can't, I only took half day off.

185
00:18:49,690 --> 00:18:50,920
I will be back sooner this evening.

186
00:18:53,010 --> 00:18:54,011
You should rest.

187
00:20:19,623 --> 00:20:20,624
Shen,

188
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:22,700
I need to talk to you.

189
00:20:23,870 --> 00:20:25,240
Why did you have to lock the door?

190
00:20:26,110 --> 00:20:27,240
I don't want anyone to disturb us.

191
00:20:28,474 --> 00:20:29,475
I need to talk to you about the baby.

192
00:20:31,603 --> 00:20:34,160
It was my first baby.

193
00:20:34,892 --> 00:20:36,440
It was supposed to be my parents' first grandchild.

194
00:20:37,720 --> 00:20:38,721
Everybody was anticipated to see it.

195
00:20:40,077 --> 00:20:41,640
It was gone

196
00:20:41,678 --> 00:20:42,679
because of your carelessness.

197
00:20:44,263 --> 00:20:45,840
I am sorry about that.

198
00:20:47,590 --> 00:20:49,320
Don't you think it is too easy to say sorry?

199
00:20:50,150 --> 00:20:52,151
I think you need to do more to own up for it.

200
00:20:53,120 --> 00:20:54,640
What do you want me to do?

201
00:20:55,800 --> 00:20:57,200
Have another baby for me.

202
00:21:00,500 --> 00:21:02,800
Help! Help me! Help!

203
00:21:14,890 --> 00:21:16,560
Help! Help!

204
00:21:21,230 --> 00:21:22,231
Who is in there?

205
00:21:23,240 --> 00:21:25,441
Help! Help!

206
00:21:28,183 --> 00:21:29,184
Shen? Is that you?

207
00:21:29,717 --> 00:21:31,080
Shin, get the key.

208
00:21:39,540 --> 00:21:41,000
Why are you interrupting me?

209
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:44,090
Do you have any idea what you just did?

210
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:46,100
She is your brother's wife.

211
00:21:47,317 --> 00:21:48,318
Well, she flirted with me.

212
00:21:48,877 --> 00:21:51,240
Not true, he's lying.

213
00:21:51,312 --> 00:21:52,520
He is a liar.

214
00:21:56,003 --> 00:21:57,004
You need to be quiet.

215
00:21:58,617 --> 00:22:00,000
I don't know what the true story is.

216
00:22:00,843 --> 00:22:02,520
But nobody can find out about this,

217
00:22:03,210 --> 00:22:04,880
especially Perm and Rayrai.

218
00:22:06,250 --> 00:22:09,360
I will take care of Term, you hear me?

219
00:22:10,523 --> 00:22:12,040
DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

220
00:22:13,683 --> 00:22:14,684
Sure.

221
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:17,180
Go! Get out of here.

222
00:22:23,320 --> 00:22:24,321
Not so fast.

223
00:22:24,563 --> 00:22:26,640
What? Nothing happened, okay?

224
00:22:28,950 --> 00:22:30,400
You have never changed, not one bit.

225
00:22:31,323 --> 00:22:33,324
I thought that marriage could fix you.

226
00:22:33,520 --> 00:22:34,600
Instead, you're behaving worse

227
00:22:34,621 --> 00:22:36,320
and you tried to rape your own sister-in-law.

228
00:22:37,497 --> 00:22:38,600
This is my order.

229
00:22:39,243 --> 00:22:40,920
You can't touch Shen ever again.

230
00:22:41,680 --> 00:22:44,120
I don't want to see siblings killing one another because of a woman.

231
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:46,120
Fine, this is noted.

232
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:47,680
Are you done lecturing me?

233
00:22:48,330 --> 00:22:51,040
Don't you forget that

234
00:22:51,190 --> 00:22:53,160
we need to be grateful for Rayrai's father, a lot.

235
00:22:53,577 --> 00:22:55,120
Keep that in mind.

236
00:22:57,877 --> 00:22:58,878
Sure.

237
00:23:09,577 --> 00:23:11,160
- Shin.
- Yes, ma'am.

238
00:23:15,257 --> 00:23:17,258
You need to keep your mouth shut.

239
00:23:17,897 --> 00:23:20,200
Don't say anything to anyone, ever.

240
00:23:20,890 --> 00:23:21,891
Yes, ma'am.

241
00:23:22,040 --> 00:23:24,520
I won't tell anyone about this scandal for sure.

242
00:23:45,317 --> 00:23:47,403
Perm! Why are you keep staring at them?

243
00:23:47,590 --> 00:23:49,700
- You're jealous?
- None of your business.

244
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:55,121
Why are you jealous of them? Your wife is way more beautiful.

245
00:23:55,360 --> 00:23:57,240
- Stop talking already!
- Perm! Perm!

246
00:23:57,843 --> 00:23:58,844
Calm down.

247
00:23:58,920 --> 00:24:00,160
I don't know what the hell is wrong with him?

248
00:24:08,103 --> 00:24:10,800
- Get inside.
- What?

249
00:24:11,017 --> 00:24:13,520
I really want to talk to you all day.

250
00:24:13,730 --> 00:24:15,400
I can't keep it by myself.

251
00:24:15,800 --> 00:24:17,103
But you need to promise me

252
00:24:17,470 --> 00:24:18,918
that you can't tell a single soul

253
00:24:19,138 --> 00:24:20,572
after I tell you the secret.

254
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:21,840
If it is so confidential, then

255
00:24:21,860 --> 00:24:22,881
I don't want to know about it.

256
00:24:22,901 --> 00:24:25,000
No, you have to. I want to tell you even though

257
00:24:25,020 --> 00:24:26,021
you don't want to hear it.

258
00:24:26,130 --> 00:24:27,700
If I keep this to myself any longer,

259
00:24:27,877 --> 00:24:29,440
I will be a dead man for sure.

260
00:24:30,103 --> 00:24:31,240
Can you please listen to me?

261
00:24:32,643 --> 00:24:34,480
Sure, spill.

262
00:24:36,560 --> 00:24:39,560
Mr. Term tried to rape Ms. Shen this afternoon.

263
00:25:33,977 --> 00:25:34,978
Ms. Shen.

264
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:37,837
How did you get here?

265
00:25:38,141 --> 00:25:40,080
Your husband are at the party tonight, he isn't here yet.

266
00:25:41,630 --> 00:25:42,631
Ms. Shen.

267
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:44,880
- You can't do this.
- I know.

268
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:47,481
But I am so worried about you.

269
00:25:48,763 --> 00:25:50,120
I know what happened today.

270
00:25:51,863 --> 00:25:52,864
About what?

271
00:25:55,040 --> 00:25:57,041
- Nothing happened today.
- Ms. Shen.

272
00:25:58,383 --> 00:25:59,500
Don't you lie to me.

273
00:26:02,500 --> 00:26:04,300
How did Mr. Term hurt you?

274
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,680
I don't want to talk about it.

275
00:26:17,923 --> 00:26:19,080
Don't you worry.

276
00:26:20,960 --> 00:26:22,050
If he tries to do anything to you next time,

277
00:26:22,343 --> 00:26:24,100
I will protect you.

278
00:26:25,300 --> 00:26:26,700
I am worried about you.

279
00:26:30,163 --> 00:26:31,720
It is not your job.

280
00:26:33,537 --> 00:26:34,600
And our bedroom

281
00:26:35,523 --> 00:26:37,080
is not your place either.

282
00:26:44,120 --> 00:26:45,121
I am sorry.

283
00:26:47,600 --> 00:26:49,640
I shouldn't have done anything that it wasn't place.

284
00:26:52,070 --> 00:26:53,280
I am just a car driver.

285
00:26:57,263 --> 00:26:58,840
But I really want you to know that

286
00:26:59,510 --> 00:27:01,080
I will be by your side forever.

287
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:04,920
I am willing to do anything for you.

288
00:27:11,057 --> 00:27:12,058
No need to.

289
00:27:15,977 --> 00:27:16,978
I don't want it.

290
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:23,640
Shen! Open the door!

291
00:27:25,001 --> 00:27:26,002
Shen!

292
00:27:27,243 --> 00:27:28,244
Open the door!

293
00:27:32,663 --> 00:27:33,664
Go!

294
00:27:34,577 --> 00:27:35,578
Shen!

295
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:37,241
Shen!

296
00:27:39,063 --> 00:27:40,064
Shen!

297
00:27:47,303 --> 00:27:48,564
Why do you have to lock the door?

298
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:52,080
I was taking a bath so I locked the door.

299
00:27:53,850 --> 00:27:54,851
Yeah?

300
00:27:57,743 --> 00:27:59,310
Have you been drinking again?

301
00:27:59,383 --> 00:28:00,384
None of your business.

302
00:28:04,677 --> 00:28:05,678
Well…

303
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:08,320
- I should find a cold cloth for you…
- No need to.

304
00:28:10,320 --> 00:28:12,720
I'm not that drunk.

305
00:28:14,270 --> 00:28:15,640
Did you...

306
00:28:16,743 --> 00:28:18,400
wear your shoes to the bedroom?

307
00:28:21,150 --> 00:28:22,151
Huh?

308
00:28:24,497 --> 00:28:27,280
After dinner, I went for a walk in the garden.

309
00:28:27,840 --> 00:28:30,120
I saw that my shoes were muddy so I brought them here to clean.

310
00:28:30,750 --> 00:28:32,920
It could be the stain.

311
00:28:35,577 --> 00:28:37,280
I didn't expect such a long answer for a short question.

312
00:29:27,543 --> 00:29:29,360
I am willing to do anything for you.

313
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:33,961
No need to.

314
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:36,281
I don't want it.

315
00:29:56,520 --> 00:29:57,521
Come in.

316
00:30:10,777 --> 00:30:11,778
Mr. Perm.

317
00:30:12,010 --> 00:30:13,011
What's up?

318
00:30:14,590 --> 00:30:16,120
I'd like to resign, sir.

319
00:30:20,037 --> 00:30:21,300
I want to go back to Penang

320
00:30:22,263 --> 00:30:23,464
and help out with my family business.

321
00:30:33,090 --> 00:30:34,091
Why?

322
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:36,440
Is there any problem?

323
00:30:40,520 --> 00:30:42,200
I think that I'm not the right man for this job,

324
00:30:42,921 --> 00:30:45,320
the one that you assigned me to do.

325
00:30:53,083 --> 00:30:56,160
Where is Tone? Why doesn't he show up for lunch?

326
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:57,681
That's right.

327
00:30:58,280 --> 00:30:59,400
The car is still here.

328
00:31:00,343 --> 00:31:02,640
I think he needs to talk to Mr. Perm in his office.

329
00:31:08,217 --> 00:31:09,440
You can't resign.

330
00:31:10,883 --> 00:31:12,480
I gave your family a lot of money,

331
00:31:13,480 --> 00:31:15,520
otherwise your mom would have been paralyzed by now.

332
00:31:18,120 --> 00:31:20,600
You still need to send money for her medical bills every month.

333
00:31:20,883 --> 00:31:22,040
If you weren't working for me,

334
00:31:22,997 --> 00:31:24,760
how would you manage to pay the bills?

335
00:31:35,263 --> 00:31:36,264
You are the right man for this job.

336
00:31:37,023 --> 00:31:38,920
It is not beyond your ability.

337
00:31:59,890 --> 00:32:00,891
Tone.

338
00:32:01,840 --> 00:32:03,880
- Mr. Perm.
- Wait, Tone.

339
00:32:04,840 --> 00:32:08,040
You can't forget me when we're apart.

340
00:32:09,280 --> 00:32:10,281
I won't forget you.

341
00:32:11,103 --> 00:32:13,104
You will forever be my boss.

342
00:32:14,120 --> 00:32:17,401
And you will forever be my friend.

343
00:32:18,280 --> 00:32:19,600
When I grow up,

344
00:32:20,100 --> 00:32:22,458
can I come back to work for you?

345
00:32:23,240 --> 00:32:24,241
Promise?

346
00:32:59,250 --> 00:33:02,720
We were lucky that he didn't question much last night.

347
00:33:05,537 --> 00:33:06,538
Yes, ma'am.

348
00:33:07,783 --> 00:33:09,840
I won't do that such thing again.

349
00:33:13,503 --> 00:33:15,520
You can't be here me anymore.

350
00:33:16,937 --> 00:33:18,800
When I am out or buying stuff,

351
00:33:19,357 --> 00:33:21,120
you don't have to follow me around and carry stuff for me.

352
00:33:23,080 --> 00:33:25,750
I'm married and I have a husband.

353
00:33:26,990 --> 00:33:29,080
My husband is your boss.

354
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:35,560
What happened at the party the other night

355
00:33:37,270 --> 00:33:38,720
was a mistake.

356
00:33:40,610 --> 00:33:42,360
And it won't happen again.

357
00:33:46,560 --> 00:33:47,561
Yes, ma'am.

358
00:34:21,730 --> 00:34:23,360
- Ms. Sales Associate?
- Yes, ma'am?

359
00:34:25,643 --> 00:34:28,360
I am looking for perfume for my husband, any suggestions?

360
00:34:29,040 --> 00:34:31,720
Can you describe your husband for me?

361
00:34:31,737 --> 00:34:33,240
I can pick the right scent for him.

362
00:34:34,097 --> 00:34:37,000
He is 28 years old, tall,

363
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:38,700
good-looking man

364
00:34:39,200 --> 00:34:40,760
and he works at the Ministry of Commerce.

365
00:34:41,201 --> 00:34:42,840
I am buying him a gift.

366
00:34:45,560 --> 00:34:48,080
What about this one? It is imported from France.

367
00:34:48,161 --> 00:34:51,080
There are a few bottles available and this is the last one.

368
00:34:52,200 --> 00:34:53,201
Please give me your wrist.

369
00:34:57,897 --> 00:34:58,898
Do you like it?

370
00:34:59,240 --> 00:35:00,100
Sales associate.

371
00:35:02,857 --> 00:35:03,858
Khunying Anongnuch, hello.

372
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:06,801
I am looking for a male perfume.

373
00:35:07,450 --> 00:35:10,640
I'd like to thank him for being my dance partner the other night.

374
00:35:11,070 --> 00:35:12,271
Do you have any suggestions?

375
00:35:12,450 --> 00:35:13,680
Just a moment, Khunying.

376
00:35:15,317 --> 00:35:16,318
And this one.

377
00:35:16,600 --> 00:35:17,760
This scent…

378
00:35:18,303 --> 00:35:19,304
which one is it?

379
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:21,800
It is this one.

380
00:35:22,863 --> 00:35:25,600
I like the smell, I will take this one.

381
00:35:26,297 --> 00:35:29,240
But…the lady…

382
00:35:30,530 --> 00:35:32,880
Hi, Shen.

383
00:35:33,583 --> 00:35:35,360
How long have you been here?

384
00:35:36,164 --> 00:35:39,080
I didn't see you here. Did you see her?

385
00:35:39,943 --> 00:35:41,800
- Nope.
- No, I didn't.

386
00:35:43,080 --> 00:35:45,081
- I'll take this one.
- Sure.

387
00:35:45,550 --> 00:35:46,551
How could you?

388
00:35:47,223 --> 00:35:49,100
Didn't you see that I bought it first?

389
00:35:50,203 --> 00:35:51,204
How much?

390
00:35:52,057 --> 00:35:53,200
85 baht, ma'am.

391
00:36:06,997 --> 00:36:07,998
Put it in a bag.

392
00:36:10,177 --> 00:36:11,840
I told you to put it in the bag.

393
00:36:12,720 --> 00:36:13,721
Sure, ma'am.

394
00:36:19,990 --> 00:36:22,280
You like it, don't you? Stealing from others.

395
00:36:23,520 --> 00:36:24,640
Who did you just berate?

396
00:36:24,770 --> 00:36:25,880
I didn't mean anyone in particular,

397
00:36:26,183 --> 00:36:27,720
then someone jumped to conclusion.

398
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:30,240
I will buy some rice bran after this

399
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:32,560
to feed fish in the temple.

400
00:36:33,240 --> 00:36:36,400
If you want to take some of them from me, you can follow me.

401
00:36:37,160 --> 00:36:38,161
Hey!

402
00:36:42,457 --> 00:36:43,458
Hey!

403
00:36:45,640 --> 00:36:47,360
- Shen, you bitch!
- That's enough.

404
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:49,760
Don't waste your energy on someone unworthy.

405
00:36:57,723 --> 00:36:58,724
Ms. Shen?

406
00:37:00,120 --> 00:37:01,840
- Go home.
- What happened?

407
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:03,283
None of your business.

408
00:37:03,407 --> 00:37:04,840
Ms. Shen, please tell me.

409
00:37:05,120 --> 00:37:06,121
I want to go home.

410
00:37:06,373 --> 00:37:07,800
- But…
- Tone!

411
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:10,300
I told you that I needed to go home.

412
00:37:41,617 --> 00:37:42,618
Tone,

413
00:37:43,650 --> 00:37:44,480
you should take a break.

414
00:37:44,570 --> 00:37:46,321
You've been working out for hours, you must be tired.

415
00:37:46,543 --> 00:37:47,544
Come on.

416
00:37:52,037 --> 00:37:54,120
You're so sweaty, so soaked up.

417
00:37:54,237 --> 00:37:55,520
- Have some water.
- Thank you.

418
00:37:56,680 --> 00:37:59,240
Hey! Stop disturbing him already.

419
00:37:59,350 --> 00:38:00,640
Disturbing what?

420
00:38:00,777 --> 00:38:03,400
We were just watching him box, that's it.

421
00:38:04,250 --> 00:38:06,920
Tone is so strong, unlike someone.

422
00:38:07,520 --> 00:38:09,920
Hey! What do you mean by that?

423
00:38:10,290 --> 00:38:11,630
Are you picking a fight with me?

424
00:38:11,910 --> 00:38:14,440
About what? I didn't mention anyone.

425
00:38:14,650 --> 00:38:17,603
You didn't say the name but you looked at me.

426
00:38:18,683 --> 00:38:20,440
Nobody wants to talk to you.

427
00:38:20,550 --> 00:38:22,360
- You're so full of yourself.
- That's right.

428
00:38:22,551 --> 00:38:23,560
Such a smart mouth.

429
00:38:23,737 --> 00:38:25,600
You're so tiny. I can hang you like a punching bag

430
00:38:25,638 --> 00:38:26,639
and punch you.

431
00:39:15,950 --> 00:39:16,951
Where is Shen?

432
00:39:18,610 --> 00:39:19,800
I asked where she is!

433
00:39:20,437 --> 00:39:21,720
She is at the terrace.

434
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:28,761
Honey?

435
00:39:28,803 --> 00:39:29,804
Come with me.

436
00:39:30,200 --> 00:39:32,320
- Where to?
- What mess did you cause yesterday?

437
00:39:34,330 --> 00:39:36,120
- About Khunying Anongnuch?
- Damn right!

438
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:38,840
People at the Ministry told me already. You need to apologize.

439
00:39:39,057 --> 00:39:40,758
You're not going to listen to my side of the story?

440
00:39:40,800 --> 00:39:42,120
There is nothing to hear. Let's go.

441
00:39:49,397 --> 00:39:51,372
- What happened?
- None of your business.

442
00:39:51,903 --> 00:39:52,904
Get in!

443
00:39:52,990 --> 00:39:54,160
Duang, you need to drive fast.

444
00:39:54,480 --> 00:39:55,481
- Yes, sir.
- Go!

445
00:40:25,400 --> 00:40:26,920
Can you fix a better facial expression?

446
00:40:28,443 --> 00:40:29,520
You're here to apologize to her.

447
00:40:56,797 --> 00:40:57,798
Nuch,

448
00:40:58,360 --> 00:40:59,600
I bring Shen here to apologize to you,

449
00:40:59,783 --> 00:41:00,960
she realizes that what she did was wrong.

450
00:41:19,790 --> 00:41:21,400
If I need to apologize for slapping your face,

451
00:41:22,080 --> 00:41:23,440
you need to apologize to me too.

452
00:41:23,863 --> 00:41:25,200
Because you slapped me first.

453
00:41:25,457 --> 00:41:26,458
Shen!

454
00:41:30,097 --> 00:41:31,198
Such a smart mouth.

455
00:41:32,690 --> 00:41:34,760
My dad hasn't heard about any of this.

456
00:41:36,200 --> 00:41:37,640
If you want me to apologize to you,

457
00:41:38,270 --> 00:41:40,480
I think I need to discuss it with him first.

458
00:41:40,930 --> 00:41:42,500
By that time,

459
00:41:42,897 --> 00:41:44,600
you wouldn't be just apologizing to me

460
00:41:45,923 --> 00:41:48,000
but my dad could do anything worse to you.

461
00:41:49,457 --> 00:41:53,000
I'm not sure if any of this

462
00:41:54,090 --> 00:41:55,240
could affect Perm's career.

463
00:41:59,990 --> 00:42:00,991
Well,

464
00:42:01,483 --> 00:42:04,050
it seems like my dad is looking for a new Permanent Secretary.

465
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:08,240
I heard that so many talented people catch his attention.

466
00:42:10,160 --> 00:42:11,920
I'm not sure who will be the very first ones

467
00:42:13,040 --> 00:42:14,041
to be eliminated.

468
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:26,881
I'm sorry.

469
00:42:31,120 --> 00:42:32,560
You slapped me so hard

470
00:42:32,897 --> 00:42:34,360
but this was how you apologized to me?

471
00:42:37,280 --> 00:42:38,920
If you bow down to your knees,

472
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:40,761
that would be more appropriate.

473
00:43:11,920 --> 00:43:13,040
Perm.

474
00:43:15,030 --> 00:43:16,400
Come here and sit with me.

475
00:43:21,870 --> 00:43:23,760
I bought you a perfume.

476
00:43:24,683 --> 00:43:25,800
I spent such a long time selecting

477
00:43:25,840 --> 00:43:27,700
the one that would suit you the most.

478
00:43:28,640 --> 00:43:30,360
Do you want to sniff it? I'll spray some for you.

479
00:43:31,120 --> 00:43:32,121
Sure.

480
00:43:39,920 --> 00:43:40,921
It smells nice.

481
00:43:46,840 --> 00:43:47,880
It smells really nice.

482
00:43:51,670 --> 00:43:52,960
Perm, dear.

483
00:43:53,557 --> 00:43:55,600
My dad won't be home tomorrow.

484
00:43:55,803 --> 00:43:57,560
I will be so lonely.

485
00:43:58,363 --> 00:44:00,600
Can you come to dinner with me?

486
00:44:01,520 --> 00:44:02,521
Sure, I can.

487
00:44:03,110 --> 00:44:04,200
And…

488
00:44:05,683 --> 00:44:07,520
don't bring anyone with you.

489
00:44:27,280 --> 00:44:28,281
What are you doing?

490
00:44:32,530 --> 00:44:34,000
I am useless to you.

491
00:44:34,130 --> 00:44:36,600
- Why do you still want me here?
- I want you as my wife.

492
00:44:37,023 --> 00:44:38,920
You're precious to me, I still need you.

493
00:44:39,600 --> 00:44:40,601
Precious?

494
00:44:41,010 --> 00:44:43,600
And you acted so close and cozy to Nuch right in front of me.

495
00:44:43,777 --> 00:44:46,000
- And I am precious to you?
- I see her as a sister.

496
00:44:46,377 --> 00:44:47,560
She is a daughter of my boss.

497
00:44:48,320 --> 00:44:50,520
What would happen if she decided to tell on you?

498
00:44:51,250 --> 00:44:53,040
I did that because I was worried for you.

499
00:44:54,437 --> 00:44:56,360
No, you were more worried about your career.

500
00:44:57,383 --> 00:44:59,680
You took her side and I need to bow to her feet.

501
00:45:00,537 --> 00:45:02,880
You didn't even ask me what happened.

502
00:45:03,423 --> 00:45:05,600
You didn't even care how hurtful I was.

503
00:45:06,963 --> 00:45:08,760
If you really needed to suck up that bitch

504
00:45:08,864 --> 00:45:10,265
and you ignored my feelings like this,

505
00:45:10,443 --> 00:45:12,700
you should just divorce me and marry her instead.

506
00:45:15,040 --> 00:45:16,141
Stop talking to me like that.

507
00:45:17,160 --> 00:45:18,300
I am your husband.

508
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:20,320
You need to respect me.

509
00:45:23,200 --> 00:45:24,400
I am your wife.

510
00:45:25,800 --> 00:45:26,960
You don't need to respect me

511
00:45:27,440 --> 00:45:29,000
and you can abuse me all you want?

512
00:45:30,490 --> 00:45:31,880
You spoke to me harshly first.

513
00:45:32,960 --> 00:45:34,080
I needed to discipline you.

514
00:45:36,770 --> 00:45:37,920
If abusing your wife

515
00:45:38,320 --> 00:45:40,840
would make you feel proud of your masculinity,

516
00:45:41,237 --> 00:45:43,440
Go ahead and slap me more!

517
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:45,001
Just slap me!

518
00:45:46,120 --> 00:45:47,121
You challenged me?

519
00:45:57,743 --> 00:45:59,840
You're right for slapping me.

520
00:46:01,757 --> 00:46:03,400
Because I am a bad wife.

521
00:46:04,290 --> 00:46:06,123
I keep on talking back to you.

522
00:46:07,197 --> 00:46:08,198
Slap me more!

523
00:46:08,530 --> 00:46:09,680
Slap me more!

524
00:46:09,810 --> 00:46:12,520
Slap me until I was injured and die! Do it!

525
00:46:12,600 --> 00:46:14,960
- Slap me until I die!
- Enough!

526
00:46:21,760 --> 00:46:23,761
Get out of my face.

527
00:46:29,710 --> 00:46:30,760
Go away!

528
00:46:33,817 --> 00:46:34,818
Go!

529
00:47:12,200 --> 00:47:13,201
Tone,

530
00:47:16,320 --> 00:47:17,680
take me to the cottage in the rice field.

531
00:47:19,840 --> 00:47:20,841
Yes, ma'am.

532
00:48:32,040 --> 00:48:33,041
Make love to me.

533
00:52:41,682 --> 00:52:42,683
I am no different

534
00:52:43,963 --> 00:52:46,883
than the little birth, Nualnoi, in a cage at the terrace.

535
00:52:50,177 --> 00:52:51,800
Since my mom passed away,

536
00:52:52,880 --> 00:52:54,560
my dad had shieled me from everything.

537
00:52:56,481 --> 00:52:58,360
He didn't let me go anywhere.

538
00:53:02,103 --> 00:53:03,480
When I got married,

539
00:53:05,443 --> 00:53:06,560
I thought that

540
00:53:06,937 --> 00:53:09,160
I would be free from that cage.

541
00:53:11,920 --> 00:53:13,200
It turned out that

542
00:53:15,297 --> 00:53:17,800
I was just moved to live in another cage.

543
00:53:23,957 --> 00:53:25,080
Today,

544
00:53:30,543 --> 00:53:32,960
you finally free me from the cage, Tone.

545
00:53:41,360 --> 00:53:42,680
I told you already

546
00:53:46,280 --> 00:53:48,181
that I can do anything for you, Ms. Shen.

547
00:54:04,281 --> 00:54:05,560
Does it still hurt?

548
00:54:17,170 --> 00:54:18,171
Ms. Shen,

549
00:54:20,600 --> 00:54:21,960
please stop crying.

550
00:54:25,497 --> 00:54:27,080
You still have me, I am right here.

551
00:55:47,877 --> 00:55:48,878
Where have you been?

552
00:55:49,577 --> 00:55:50,920
Why are you home so late.

553
00:55:53,730 --> 00:55:55,400
I went home to see my dad.

554
00:55:56,637 --> 00:55:57,840
I need a shower.

555
00:57:17,670 --> 00:57:18,880
- Aunt Erb.
- Yes, sir?

556
00:57:19,880 --> 00:57:21,120
I won't be home for dinner tonight.

557
00:57:21,217 --> 00:57:22,320
I need to have dinner with Nuch.

558
00:57:23,200 --> 00:57:24,520
Please tell mom for me.

559
00:57:24,680 --> 00:57:25,681
Sure, sir.

560
00:59:33,777 --> 00:59:36,280
He is not the same guy that I used to know.

561
00:59:38,240 --> 00:59:39,441
As a matter of fact,

562
00:59:40,457 --> 00:59:42,360
maybe I have never known him.

563
00:59:46,283 --> 00:59:48,160
Please don't change, Tone.

564
00:59:53,907 --> 00:59:54,908
Never,

565
01:00:08,240 --> 01:00:09,560
I will never change.

566
01:00:58,563 --> 01:01:00,320
I wish I had a superpower.

567
01:01:00,920 --> 01:01:02,640
I want to freeze this moment.

568
01:01:03,360 --> 01:01:05,120
I don't have any superpower

569
01:01:05,497 --> 01:01:07,303
but I will love you

570
01:01:07,880 --> 01:01:09,400
as long as you want.

571
01:01:14,430 --> 01:01:16,240
I'm here to warn you about Tone.

572
01:01:16,520 --> 01:01:18,200
I see that Shen is going out with him every day.

573
01:01:18,377 --> 01:01:20,640
They both are young and it could lead to scandal.

574
01:01:21,157 --> 01:01:22,600
Do you have anything to tell me?
